Small visual novel about a girl who dislikes her name with some Ghost Whisperer parts.

Pros:
- It's free;
- Wonderfull artwork;
- Music is in tune;
- Yuri ( if you into that - no fanservice)
- Has achievements;
- nice plot twists;

Cons:
- Too short;
- some parts the feein train will make a stop or two.

Overall great work of the devs , who made this game for free
